# Redactor Character Count plugin

Redactor does not lend itself well to character counting out of the box. This plugin aims to add easy support for character counting and maximum character limitation functionality.

* version - 0.1
* homepage - [http://github.com/staycassiopeia/redactor-character-count/](http://github.com/staycassiopeia/redactor-character-count/)
* author - [Brandon Scott](http://www.brandonandrewscott.com)

